		<description><![CDATA[One day a more indept study of Bernadette and her super concious visions will come to light.  Many think that she was singlely graced by God and she was a diamond soul and very advanced being.  The wonderful fact is we too can commune with the Divine/.  St. Francis saw Jesus in vision every night and cured the sick and raised the dead even though he was beset with many ailments.  There are many others and many not known to the world but to God alone.  Ramakrishna a great saint of India would daily go into ecstatic samadhi or God Communion.
.]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>One day a more indept study of Bernadette and her super concious visions will come to light.  Many think that she was singlely graced by God and she was a diamond soul and very advanced being.  The wonderful fact is we too can commune with the Divine/.  St. Francis saw Jesus in vision every night and cured the sick and raised the dead even though he was beset with many ailments.  There are many others and many not known to the world but to God alone.  Ramakrishna a great saint of India would daily go into ecstatic samadhi or God Communion.<br />
.</p>
