		<description><![CDATA[Definitely many seers were persecuted as heretics. Bernadette herself faced strong skepticism from churchmen; that she was able to break through is testimony to the power of her vision. There must have been others in the centuries before who sank under the weight of repression.]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Definitely many seers were persecuted as heretics. Bernadette herself faced strong skepticism from churchmen; that she was able to break through is testimony to the power of her vision. There must have been others in the centuries before who sank under the weight of repression.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
